d in the beta let's you enjoy yourself as you munch on s'mores and unwind from a stressful day.", "short_description": "*Discounted price while in Beta. New gameplay, environments, and food are included in the roadmap for the full release.*\n\nEnjoy a delightful delicacy of roasted marshmallow, melted chocolate, and graham cracker as you relax by a warm campfire and listen to the peaceful babble from a nearby brook.\n\nAs the name suggests, S'more Please let's you cook s'mores! The relaxing gamemode included in the beta let's you enjoy yourself as you munch on s'mores and unwind from a stressful day."}]}, "developer_name": "Mischief Game Dev", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mobilemischief.net/smore-please/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Mischief Game Dev", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://mobilemischief.net/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SIMULATION", "FOOD", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1258801801364764"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-sin6-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75500282_466234222382372_4390445270671731386_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NSqWUEaFBYsQ7kNvgEeKiR3&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB244iync-w2xNx82DCxr0EoYTJePNBvmXzA6jGnkNU8Q&oe=6728BE66"}